Special Thanks to HTC Vive for Sponsoring this episode and allowing US to Give Away a HTC VIVE! 
Vote Now in the VDA Community Choice Awards ► http://bit.ly/VDA16CC

Voting for the VDA Community Choice Awards is now open. So we thought we'd show off some of the nominees and play play some VR Minigolf. We are sinking our balls like pros! And by the end of the episode one lucky viewer wins a brand new HTC VIVE! Don't forget to go vote before December 18th 2016.
